{"tid":959430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【情報】中共陸軍發布「地表最強」2018宣傳片 場面震撼","createTime":"2018-12-28T14:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T19:52:31.000Z","uid":51665,"like":12,"dislike":86,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"37cc634e31577aa2fd6a00f47cd2bd02cc194e16","tid":959430,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201812/9e81e8047f7f5960cb978da9560fc77a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201812%2F9e81e8047f7f5960cb978da9560fc77a.JPG&h=8a186144&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中共解放軍陸軍近日發布2018年度宣傳片，與往年宣傳片使用相同標題「地表最強」，<br />\n影片中各式新式武器齊出亮相，節奏明快、場面頗具震撼效果。大陸網民大量回應稱讚<br />\n，有網民激動表示共軍曾打敗日本鬼子、美國及其狗腿、蘇聯紅軍與兩個世界第三軍事<br />\n強國時，立即有網友出面糾正「日本鬼子可不是解放軍打敗的」。<br />\n<br />\n這部中共陸軍的宣傳片沿用過去數年宣傳片的標題《地表最強》，影片附帶說明指出，<br />\n今年12月31日是陸軍領導機構組建成立3周年，因此隆重發佈2018年度宣傳片，展示中共陸軍3年轉型建設成果。<br />\n<br />\n陸證實數百公里外探測到F22 將研發新攻擊武器<br />\n<br />\n共軍監測F-22？ 美媒：是真的！但情況沒那麼單純<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201812/0709f5c6eea916af4749d6aa3c58b8d9.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201812%2F0709f5c6eea916af4749d6aa3c58b8d9.JPG&h=537225dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中共陸軍航空兵直升機。（圖／影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n宣傳片附帶說明指出，步兵、裝甲、炮兵、陸航、特種部隊等陸軍十大兵種告別傳統數<br />\n量規模型，向著編製小型化、能力多樣化、編成模塊化轉變；空中突擊、情報偵察、電<br />\n子對抗、多兵種合成等新型作戰力量逐漸成為陸軍未來戰場的尖刀鐵拳；遠程火箭炮系<br />\n統、新型武裝直升機、電子偵察車等多種現役主戰裝備悉數亮相。<br />\n<br />\n此外，未來中共陸軍將按照機動作戰、立體攻防的戰略要求，優化力量編成和規模結構<br />\n，遵循資訊主導、體系支撐、精兵作戰、聯合制勝的現代戰爭理念，加速由區域防衛型<br />\n向全域作戰型轉變。<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201812/7b7850b2ad8b81ecbaf533367806bb8f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201812%2F7b7850b2ad8b81ecbaf533367806bb8f.JPG&h=66fe97d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中共陸軍步兵戰車。（圖／影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n這部宣傳片製作相當精細，剪接節奏明快、配樂激盪、場面頗具震撼效果，獲得了許多<br />\n大陸網友稱讚，直稱「看的我熱血沸騰」，「等轟20出來後就更好看更牛逼了」、「中<br />\n國軍隊，無論軍規、軍紀、作戰能力、軍人素質、和無畏強敵的精神，地球上找不出第<br />\n二個國家可以匹敵」。<br />\n<br />\n還有網民看完影片激動地表示：「不管我人民解放軍是不是地表最強！但我們知道我人<br />\n民解放軍打敗過──日本鬼子、美國及另外十五個狗腿子、蘇聯紅軍、兩個世界第三軍<br />\n事強國！」但立即有其他網民回應「日本鬼子可不是解放軍打敗的」、「解放軍打敗日<br />\n本？是那部劇？」顯然抗日戰爭的史實雖經扭曲，仍有不少人非常在意歷史真相。<br />\n<br />\n另有網民說，「地表最強，強在哪裡？強在軍隊性質！強在軍人精神！&hellip;&hellip;其他的，還<br />\n要努力！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YXyuh5lXAYc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYXyuh5lXAYc&d=K43woMbQiM9c16wEEDxDM9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=2018aa18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YXyuh5lXAYc</a><br />\n厲害了我的國 征服世界不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3dbef0c619676eb837730c7164f5dec605c44c1","tid":959430,"uid":79563,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:42:53.000Z","msg":"地表最強山寨貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084f8586a99226e384c9a772e3063685ddb8fa8e","tid":959430,"uid":132302,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又可以打飛機"},{"pid":"5dae6fab5815220293adfc5730c4450258c2b440","tid":959430,"uid":60366,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:46:14.000Z","msg":"未出發先出精<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702a37f5edd860322d22936a9cc9d7d850bb1809","tid":959430,"uid":51665,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:48:10.000Z","msg":"收到風習大大從外星人手上得到太空科技可以屌打全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f593dfd3de6d1f32c273892dd19dc305eefc400f","tid":959430,"uid":40052,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:52:43.000Z","msg":"有自信係好事 都要睇環境㗎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今晚侵仔成晚唔訓係咁抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00a514bdf82fbd3187695f6c1aaf396f27f4cdf","tid":959430,"uid":73909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:53:16.000Z","msg":"厲害了我的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5521b8c964fcfae8545b5683803efcb790e2a5dd","tid":959430,"uid":36901,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:53:45.000Z","msg":"海空最弱"},{"pid":"5f1dfe6be17a1a3b128d52bd88a54dd99745b25a","tid":959430,"uid":7699,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:54:29.000Z","msg":"姐撚咩地表最強<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63559f07b54b876b1239b01cf32e7ecea787c7f8","tid":959430,"uid":49853,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://replygif.net/i/128.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Freplygif.net%2Fi%2F128.gif&h=f1c56092&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8aca1833adb6c21ad5220a456109246785f7bfd0","tid":959430,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5521b8c964fcfae8545b5683803efcb790e2a5dd","tid":959430,"uid":36901,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:53:45.000Z","msg":"海空最弱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:55:34.000Z","msg":"陸軍坦克死火 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77574defbd6f40ca66cde0ba980a0f5e1fa9b560","tid":959430,"uid":219614,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:55:37.000Z","msg":"而家既解放軍的確係打得贏80年前既皇軍既"},{"pid":"f7a5c6732d6313765de17bb9225342c3dcbd06e9","tid":959430,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:55:42.000Z","msg":"j到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2