osad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T15:21:02.000Z","msg":"呢D就係佢地既高級黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d6a86dfedbc794536fcf604de5956af268948c","tid":959430,"uid":46245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T15:24:46.000Z","msg":"算低調啦，人地甄子單都自稱宇宙最強啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc33f63f48776f41f3086d0f19777631a7b45a5","tid":959430,"uid":57023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a51aca85cbee0b1a8db1ee8c5e1dea6d2522e73","tid":959430,"uid":34666,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"臭閪支那解手軍做到步兵1人1件避彈衣先學人打飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T00:48:28.000Z","msg":"仲係較落後，好似仍用幾十年前高炮榴炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21620c3ba39f45315560ece52b935cdf17562340","tid":959430,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T00:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8199c1dff31e423c9d11101085b89f857c6ff774","tid":959430,"uid":37666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T01:01:59.000Z","msg":"係咩 咁最近打過啲咩勝仗呀"},{"pid":"8a011c671d63b572f679c93b3ead937c7bc74c8d","tid":959430,"uid":196750,"like":49,"dislike":2,"score":47,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T01:13:40.000Z","msg":"其實我ㄧ直唔明中共點向愚民解釋解放軍係韓戰同越南都取得大勝。<br />\n<br />\n戰爭勝利都有客觀標準，ㄧ係佔領敵國土地，ㄧ係獲得戰爭賠償，ㄧ係死傷少過對方。但中共係呢三點次次輸畀敵方，仲次次死多百幾萬人。<br />\n<br />\n咁唯有拎咩抽象的「戰略勝利」嚟講囉。至於點戰略勝利？哦，原來係阻止美國利用朝鮮越南做跳板，佔領中国！其實美國幾時想過佔領中国呢？從清末開始，美國只堅持門戶開放，自由貿易，幾時想過佔領中国？反而中国人爭住移民去畀美國統治！<br />\n<br />\n所以中国最愛拎美國做假想敵，只要美國唔攻占北京，解放軍點輸都係「或成最大贏家」、「陸上最強」！"},{"pid":"dc45643a70c46523faa6ce5e480656e2fb9efd02","tid":959430,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T01:50:09.000Z","msg":"自己叫自己最強<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知唔知醜"},{"pid":"1be9e86db8111faa3e6184377e093b266ef37854","tid":959430,"uid":37413,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T01:51:16.000Z","msg":"中國軍隊，無論軍規、軍紀、作戰能力、軍人素質、和無畏強敵的精神，地球上找不出第二個國家可以匹敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f1b60e231ca85d147e2623da523150ccb42649","tid":959430,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T01:52:43.000Z","msg":"美國敢拍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5fe2767eb7f5541c4f905db61d895741679c65","tid":959430,"uid":50998,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T01:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/869c44fce724d4e9017eedba044c58bb/yujiro1_R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.aolcdn.com%2Fhss%2Fstorage%2Fadam%2F869c44fce724d4e9017eedba044c58bb%2Fyujiro1_R.jpg&h=30632d7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n???"},{"pid":"659759b7b4cd5ec1176b48ae41b720934a0bfa6e","tid":959430,"uid":54852,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T01:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AnsF5z9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt